the actions that the user is permitted to take by specifying the specific permissions that have been granted to the document.</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-key=\"Dg8WYIaATvyL\">\r\n<div data-key=\"aOMy5Ki3XzOI\"><span data-key=\"CQsQqbwjrLCt\"><span data-offset-key=\"CQsQqbwjrLCt:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">File Activity</span><span data-offset-key=\"CQsQqbwjrLCt:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Provides a comprehensive record of file dynamics by tracking the history of file actions, such as uploads, modifications, and downloads.</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-key=\"Ct6yqVKJonnS\">\r\n<div data-key=\"UevHb1gyLGQA\"><span data-key=\"8vhAlHNhTVrv\"><span data-offset-key=\"8vhAlHNhTVrv:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Version History</span><span data-offset-key=\"8vhAlHNhTVrv:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Records all modifications to the file, including the modifier, modification time, and version history, for future reference.</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-key=\"lBwlC4a3f7Q6\">\r\n<div data-key=\"M5naFwSdwXBd\"><span data-key=\"43iStrf6o4bo\"><span data-offset-key=\"43iStrf6o4bo:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Related Information</span><span data-offset-key=\"43iStrf6o4bo:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> It indicates whether the file is linked to other files, which is essential for comprehending file dependencies.</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n3.3.1 Search Functionality\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSearch Overview The search functionality is conspicuously situated in the upper right quadrant of the \"File Management\" interface. It provides users with the ability to conduct rapid and precise file queries by providing access to sophisticated parameters through a drop-down menu.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nKey Features of the Search Box:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nComprehensive Text Search Facilitates exhaustive text inquiries across all documents, guaranteeing that no pertinent information is overlooked.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPinyin Search It enables users to search for files by inputting Pinyin, which is a method that is well-known to those who are accustomed to it.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSearch for the first letter It enables queries using the first letters of Pinyin, which is notably beneficial for locating folders, thereby facilitating rapid file retrieval.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCustomizing the Search Scope:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCurrent Folder/All Folders Users have the ability to determine whether the search should be limited to the current folder or extend across all folders, thereby improving the precision of the search.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFile Type Filtering:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPreset File Categories The system organizes files into folders, documents, images, music, videos, and more. Additionally, users have the ability to establish their own file formats in order to conduct more precise searches.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTime Range Search:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDate of Creation Users can simplify the process of locating files by specifying a time range for file creation, which simplifies the process of determining the date of their creation.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFile Size Filtering:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSearch Based on File Size Users can locate files of a specific size or within a defined range by filtering search results by file size.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCreator-Based Search:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDepartmental Network Disk Users have the ability to search for files that were generated by a particular individual in the enterprise environment, which is especially beneficial for team collaborations.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n3.3.2 Options for File Viewing\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFile Management View Modes Within the file administration module of the Kedao Cloud system, there are three distinct viewing modes: List View, Icon View, and Column View.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nIcon Mode Images are automatically displayed as thumbnails in this mode, in addition to a variety of file icons. Users can effortlessly modify the dimensions of the icon and organize files according to their preferences.\r\n\r\n\r\nList Mode List Mode provides a methodical approach to file management. Customizable alterations, such as the capacity to resize and drag the title bar, and the unlimited expansion of folders with subdirectories, are supported.\r\n\r\n\r\nColumn Mode Column Mode, which is modeled after the Mac OS interface, enables users to expand multi-level folders in columns. The administration of intricate folder hierarchies is substantially simplified by the ease with which files can be transferred between columns.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n3.3.3 Information (Properties) Panel\r\n\r\n\r\nAttributes Overview:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFundamental Information Displays critical file information, including the size, file count, creator/modifier, personal notes, and keywords.\r\n\r\n\r\nDocument Permissions Clarifies the actions that the user is permitted to take by specifying the specific permissions that have been granted to the document.\r\n\r\n\r\nFile Activity Provides a comprehensive record of file dynamics by tracking the history of file actions, such as uploads, modifications, and downloads.\r\n\r\n\r\nVersion History Records all modifications to the file, including the modifier, modification time, and version history, for future reference.\r\n\r\n\r\nRelated Information It indicates whether the file is linked to other files, which is essential for comprehending file dependencies.\r\n\r\n\r\n', 3, '2024-08-29 0