gation pane on the left column and select&nbsp;</span><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"Aaizhmx4gt9q:1\">\"Tag Management\"</strong><span data-offset-key=\"Aaizhmx4gt9q:2\"> to open the Tag Management Panel.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"2H4OzgwxKaVe\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"2H4OzgwxKaVe\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r r-13awgt0\">\r\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"RMj29p9Dadtk\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"ikTEQ49CAlPe\"><span data-offset-key=\"ikTEQ49CAlPe:0\">In this panel, you can create new tags, sort existing tags by dragging and dropping, and delete or perform other operations. To create a new tag, click&nbsp;</span><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"ikTEQ49CAlPe:1\">\"Create Tag\"</strong><span data-offset-key=\"ikTEQ49CAlPe:2\"> in the right-click menu or the Properties panel to access the Tag Management Panel.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-3.4.3-pinning-files\">\r\n<div data-key=\"rnxHHjdq9Wus\"><br></div>\r\n<div data-key=\"rnxHHjdq9Wus\"><br></div>\r\n<div data-key=\"rnxHHjdq9Wus\"><strong><span data-key=\"cO3X9N0rOqtl\"><span data-offset-key=\"cO3X9N0rOqtl:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">4.4.3 Pinning Files</span></span></strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-to-prioritize-import\">\r\n<div data-key=\"RfQ2ZFk9L6ir\"><br></div>\r\n<div data-key=\"RfQ2ZFk9L6ir\"><span data-key=\"bGBIjc1hnXYJ\"><span data-offset-key=\"bGBIjc1hnXYJ:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">To prioritize important files, use the pin feature:</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-select-the-file-and-\">\r\n<div data-key=\"XKfLFkVQy1S7\">\r\n<div data-key=\"BYyiz3GQA1Qq\">\r\n<div data-key=\"K9dj69xn4BEN\"><span data-key=\"zuujzaDf1Qob\"><span data-offset-key=\"zuujzaDf1Qob:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Select the file and click the </span><span data-offset-key=\"zuujzaDf1Qob:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">\"Pin\"</span><span data-offset-key=\"zuujzaDf1Qob:2\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> option from the right-click menu or toolbar. This action will keep the file easily accessible.</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-4.4.4-adding-attachm\">\r\n<div data-key=\"trR1mNIPVX7F\"><span data-key=\"drxxiwkl6kEd\"><span data-offset-key=\"drxxiwkl6kEd:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">4.4.4 Adding Attachments</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" data-slate-fragment=\"\" id=\"bkmrk-file-association-the\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"KyCvskV7PIRq\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"KyCvskV7PIRq\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"KyCvskV7PIRq\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"7skFhhxTe2fS\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"7skFhhxTe2fS:0\">File Association</strong><span data-offset-key=\"7skFhhxTe2fS:1\"> The attachment feature is used to associate files with each other, such as adding reference citations in papers. Attachments can be added directly to establish connections between related documents.</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.4.1 Favorites\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Adding Files to Favorites Kedao Cloud allows users to add files and folders to their Favorites for quick access. This feature supports the addition of various virtual directories, including user-shared content, the Recycle Bin, and personal shares.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTo add a file or folder to Favorites, click the star icon associated with the item.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n2. Removing from Favorites To remove a file or folder from Favorites, click the star icon on the saved item again to deselect it.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.4.2 File Tags\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Adding Tags Files and folders can be tagged in three ways:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDirect Drag and Drop Select one or more files or folders and drag them to the desired tag in the navigation window. This method allows for quick addition of a single tag at a time.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nRight-Click Menu/Toolbar Right-click on the file or folder or use the \"More\" option on the toolbar to access the tag options. You can add one or more tags, or remove existing tags.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nProperties/Information Panel After selecting a file or folder, tags can be added or removed through the Properties or Information panel.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n2. Managing Tags To manage tags:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nClick the drop-down menu in the tag category of the navigation pane on the left column and select\"Tag Management\" to open the Tag Management Panel.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nIn this panel, you can create new tags, sort existing tags by dragging and dropping, and delete or perform other operations. To create a new tag, click\"Create Tag\" in the right-click menu or the Properties panel to access the Tag Management Panel.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.4.3 Pinning Files\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTo prioritize important files, use the pin feature:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSelect the file and click the \"Pin\" option from the right-click menu or toolbar. This action will keep the file easily accessible.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.4.4 Adding Attachments\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFile Association The attachment feature is used to associate files with each other, such as adding reference citations in papers. Attachments can be added directly to establish connections between related documents.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 4, '2024-08-29 07:21:09', '2024-08-29 07:22:59', 1, 1, 0, '', 3, 0, NULL, 1, '');
