on performed by users. The key scenarios where document permissions are applied include:</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-department-or-public\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"TagxeDYlpGCN\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"TagxeDYlpGCN\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-4 pb-4 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"TagxeDYlpGCN\" class=\"relative flex-1\">\r\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"7tNSUpTiYqNV\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"7tNSUpTiYqNV\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r r-13awgt0\">\r\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"kS3jXBcFRAlb\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"RMd4Tm4puSHz\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"RMd4Tm4puSHz:0\">Department or Public Network Disk Permissions</strong><span data-offset-key=\"RMd4Tm4puSHz:1\">: These define a user\'s access level within a department or public network disk.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"p0VIeNU2XeMt\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"p0VIeNU2XeMt\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r r-13awgt0\">\r\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"YfiopO3VqN1G\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"WnDoVEuh6aQc\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"WnDoVEuh6aQc:0\">File or Folder Permissions</strong><span data-offset-key=\"WnDoVEuh6aQc:1\">: These specify the permissions for individual users or groups on specific documents or folders.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n