(1, 1, 'Introduction', '<p id=\"bkmrk-1.1-software-overvie\"><strong>1.1 Software Overview</strong></p>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-this-is-the-user-gui\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"IF1k2hqAZlgS\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"IF1k2hqAZlgS\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"IF1k2hqAZlgS\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"cFNZhoibcwMe\"><span data-offset-key=\"cFNZhoibcwMe:0\">This is the user guide for our web document management system. It is a powerful tool that will help you work with websites and documents more easily and quickly. This program, which used to be called Dots, is the best way to manage, share, and update papers online from a single, unified platform. </span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" data-slate-fragment=\"\" id=\"bkmrk-this-app-streamlines\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"8raa0M1mXqb0\"><span data-offset-key=\"8raa0M1mXqb0:0\">This app streamlines your work and makes you more productive, whether you\'re working on everyday documents or controlling website content directly on the server. You can use a smooth web-based method instead of old-fashioned ones like FTP if the screen is easy to use. The built-in web IDE lets you work on projects online, and the software is flexible enough to fit into any work setting.</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '1.1 Software Overview\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is the user guide for our web document management system. It is a powerful tool that will help you work with websites and documents more easily and quickly. This program, which used to be called Dots, is the best way to manage, share, and update papers online from a single, unified platform. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThis app streamlines your work and makes you more productive, whether you\'re working on everyday documents or controlling website content directly on the server. You can use a smooth web-based method instead of old-fashioned ones like FTP if the screen is easy to use. The built-in web IDE lets you work on projects online, and the software is flexible enough to fit into any work setting.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-08-29 00:06:10', '2024-08-29 00:06:10', 'introduction', 'dots-user-documentation', 'version', '', 'Initial publish', 1),
