site administration, this handbook provides guidance on properly utilizing its capabilities.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"U6xK44kHumJl\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"U6xK44kHumJl\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r r-13awgt0\">\r\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"Ntai6zVaSxhI\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"Ntai6zVaSxhI\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"t2I1Ijny7tl9\"><span data-offset-key=\"t2I1Ijny7tl9:0\">Support Teams: This guidebook contains troubleshooting hints and solutions to frequent problems to enhance your ability to assist users and provide more effective support.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '1.1 Software Overview\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is the user guide for our web document management system. It is a powerful tool that will help you work with websites and documents more easily and quickly. This program, which used to be called Dots, is the best way to manage, share, and update papers online from a single, unified platform. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThis app streamlines your work and makes you more productive, whether you\'re working on everyday documents or controlling website content directly on the server. You can use a smooth web-based method instead of old-fashioned ones like FTP if the screen is easy to use. The built-in web IDE lets you work on projects online, and the software is flexible enough to fit into any work setting.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n1.2 Purpose and Scope\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe goal of this user guide is to assist you in making the most of the document management system. There is a lot of information in this guide that will help you handle files, work with others, and keep website content up-to-date. The main things we\'ll talk about are:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nKeeping track of and sharing files with your team.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nMaking changes to and updating website material on the computer itself.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nUsing the online creation tools in the built-in web IDE.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nMaking changes to the program to make it work with your goals and the way you work.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n1.3 Intended Audience\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThis handbook is intended for all users who will engage with the program in different roles:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFor end users who are using the program for document management, sharing, or website administration, this handbook provides guidance on properly utilizing its capabilities.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSupport Teams: This guidebook contains troubleshooting hints and solutions to frequent problems to enhance your ability to assist users and provide more effective support.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-08-29 00:09:33', '2024-08-29 00:09:33', 'introduction', 'dots-user-documentation', 'version', '', '', 2),
