(8, 6, 'B. Registration', '<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-to-establish-a-new-a\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"slaLcqxFTNXV\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"slaLcqxFTNXV\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"slaLcqxFTNXV\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"HDecfxBWEEiv\"><span data-offset-key=\"HDecfxBWEEiv:0\">To establish a new account, adhere to the following procedures:</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"slaLcqxFTNXV\" class=\"relative flex-1\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" data-slate-fragment=\"\" id=\"bkmrk-begin-the-registrati\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"HY4GSwfYWLqR\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"HY4GSwfYWLqR\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-4 pb-4 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"HY4GSwfYWLqR\" class=\"relative flex-1\">\r\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"8GxOIv4kBTZi\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"8GxOIv4kBTZi\">\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"czJ9GpxJqbSq\"><span data-offset-key=\"czJ9GpxJqbSq:0\">Begin the registration process by selecting \"Register a new account\" on the login page.</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Select a Registration Method: You have the option of registering with either an email address or a mobile phone. To finalize the registration process, input the verification code that was sent to your mobile device or email.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTo establish a n