(12, 9, '3.1 Menu page', '<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-a.-overview-of-cloud\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"nE49XhCWPs4j\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"nE49XhCWPs4j\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"nE49XhCWPs4j\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"VUKE9kbFcnHy\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"VUKE9kbFcnHy:0\">A. Overview of Cloud Desktop</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"nE49XhCWPs4j\" class=\"relative flex-1\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-the-application-deli\">\r\n<div data-key=\"fUctkXIcSpIh\"><span data-key=\"FA3EVtIEvlM8\"><span data-offset-key=\"FA3EVtIEvlM8:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">The application delivers a cloud-based desktop environment that is akin to a traditional Windows desktop, and it does so directly within the web interface.</span></span></div>\r\n<div data-key=\"fUctkXIcSpIh\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-desktop-interface-us\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"wegWpcGDXTgr\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"wegWpcGDXTgr\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-4 pb-4 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"wegWpcGDXTgr\" class=\"relative flex-1\">\r\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"rgEWPNAzsQb7\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"rgEWPNAzsQb7\">\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"xU5RuRbMWx0D\"><span data-offset-key=\"xU5RuRbMWx0D:0\">Desktop Interface Users have the ability to access essential components within the cloud desktop, including My Computer, Recycle Bin, Light Applications, and Personal Center.</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Applications of Light A diverse array of lightweight applications is available in the Light Application Market. These applications can be installed at the user\'s discretion.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Customization of Desktop Wallpaper By selecting any image from the system\'s collection and selecting the \"Set as Desktop Wallpaper\" option from the right-click menu, users can customize their desktop experience.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">A Random Desktop Wallpaper The windmill icon situated in the lower right quadrant of the desktop can be clicked to activate the Random Desktop Wallpaper feature, which will automatically select a random wallpaper.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"ylr25djMpGFM\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"ylr25djMpGFM\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"ylr25djMpGFM\" class=\"relative flex-1\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk--1\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"Ndr67SeXJyRq\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"Ndr67SeXJyRq\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-4 pb-4 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"Ndr67SeXJyRq\" class=\"relative flex-1\">\r\n<div data-rnwr768-1w6e6rj-1777fci=\"true\" class=\"css-175oi2r r-18u37iz r-1777fci r-zo7nv5 r-3mtglp\">\r\n<div data-slate-void=\"true\" data-key=\"74SknoIW5ptX\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk--2\">\r\n<div