lock-content=\"KjD2FJs2LtBR\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"tedzXizZ5zEp\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"tedzXizZ5zEp:0\">C. Navigation Menu</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"KjD2FJs2LtBR\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" data-slate-fragment=\"\" id=\"bkmrk-the-menu-panel-can-b\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"BgJD2aLI1k0R\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"BgJD2aLI1k0R\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"BgJD2aLI1k0R\" class=\"relative flex-1\"></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"BgJD2aLI1k0R\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"WFY93FaEyn0l\"><span data-offset-key=\"WFY93FaEyn0l:0\">The menu panel can be accessed by users by selecting on their profile avatar within the operational interface.</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nA. Overview of Cloud Desktop\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe application delivers a cloud-based desktop environment that is akin to a traditional Windows desktop, and it does so directly within the web interface.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDesktop Interface Users have the ability to access essential components within the cloud desktop, including My Computer, Recycle Bin, Light Applications, and Personal Center.\r\nApplications of Light A diverse array of lightweight applications is available in the Light Application Market. These applications can be installed at the user\'s discretion.\r\nCustomization of Desktop Wallpaper By selecting any image from the system\'s collection and selecting the \"Set as Desktop Wallpaper\" option from the right-click menu, users can customize their desktop experience.\r\nA Random Desktop Wallpaper The windmill icon situated in the lower right quadrant of the desktop can be clicked to activate the Random Desktop Wallpaper feature, which will automatically select a random wallpaper.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nB. File Management\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFile Management Interface The file management module is intended to replicate the functionality of Windows Explorer, enabling users to manage online documents with the same simplicity and familiarity as handling files on a local Windows system.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nC. Navigation Menu\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe menu panel can be accessed by users by selecting on their profile avatar within the operational interface.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-08-29 00:33:15', '2024-08-29 00:33:15', '31-menu-page', 'dots-user-documentation', 'version', '', '', 2),
