r\n<div data-block-content=\"BgJD2aLI1k0R\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><br></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"BgJD2aLI1k0R\" class=\"relative flex-1 align-center\"><br></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"BgJD2aLI1k0R\" class=\"relative flex-1 align-center\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"WFY93FaEyn0l\"><span data-offset-key=\"WFY93FaEyn0l:0\"><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2024-08/profile.PNG\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2024-08/scaled-1680-/profile.PNG\" alt=\"Profile.PNG\"></a></span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"BgJD2aLI1k0R\" class=\"relative flex-1 align-center\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"WFY93FaEyn0l\"><span data-offset-key=\"WFY93FaEyn0l:0\"><span data-key=\"tedzXizZ5zEp\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"tedzXizZ5zEp:0\">Menu Page</strong></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"BgJD2aLI1k0R\" class=\"relative flex-1\" id=\"bkmrk--6\"></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"BgJD2aLI1k0R\" class=\"relative flex-1\" id=\"bkmrk--7\"></div>', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nA. Overview of Cloud Desktop\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe application delivers a cloud-based desktop environment that is akin to a traditional Windows desktop, and it does so directly within the web interface.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDesktop Interface Users have the ability to access essential components within the cloud desktop, including My Computer, Recycle Bin, Light Applications, and Personal Center.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDesktop page\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nApplications of Light A diverse array of lightweight applications is available in the Light Application Market. These applications can be installed at the user\'s discretion.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nLight Applications\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCustomization of Desktop Wallpaper By selecting any image from the system\'s collection and selecting the \"Set as Desktop Wallpaper\" option from the right-click menu, users can customize their desktop experience.\r\nA Random Desktop Wallpaper The windmill icon situated in the lower right quadrant of the desktop can be clicked to activate the Random Desktop Wallpaper feature, which will automatically select a random wallpaper.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDesktop Wallpaper\r\n\r\nB. File Management\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFile Management Interface The file management module is intended to replicate the functionality of Windows Explorer, enabling users to manage online documents with the same simplicity and familiarity as handling files on a local Windows system.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFile manage\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nC. Navigation Menu\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe menu panel can be accessed by users by selecting on their profile avatar within the operational interface.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nMenu Page\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-08-29 05:46:14', '2024-08-29 05:46:14', '31-menu-page', 'dots-user-documentation', 'version', '', '', 6),
(52, 18, 'D. Modify', '<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-password-after-loggi\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"nxqoJ6FCY1eh\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"nxqoJ6FCY1eh\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"nxqoJ6FCY1eh\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span data-slate-fragment=\"\">Password After logging in, you may modify your password by following these steps:</span></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"nxqoJ6FCY1eh\" class=\"relative flex-1\"></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"nxqoJ6FCY1eh\" class=\"relative flex-1\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"OTbjilhG0RaC\" id=\"bkmrk-access-account-setti\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"OTbjilhG0RaC\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-4 pb-4 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"OTbjilhG0RaC\" class=\"relative flex-1\">\r\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"ThJjwo4g0PSf\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"ThJjwo4g0PSf\">\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"null\">\r\n<p><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"DE1tPCfWugYR\"><span data-offset-key=\"DE1tPCfWugYR:0\">Access Account Settings: Click on the user avatar located in the lower-left corner of the interface.</span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">\r\n<p>Access the Personal Center: Click on \"Personal Center\" and then select \"Account Settings.\"</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">\r\n<p>Password Modification: Access the account settings page to update your password.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-\"><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2024-08/change-password.PNG\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"align-center\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2024-08/scaled-1680-/change-password.PNG\" alt=\"Change password.PNG\" width=\"622\" height=\"400\"></a></p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-modify-password\" class=\"align-center\"><strong>Modify Password</strong></p>', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPassword After logging in, you may modify your password by following these steps:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAccess Account Settings: Click on the user avatar located in the lower-left corner of the interface.\r\n\r\n\r\nAccess the Personal Center: Click on \"Personal Center\" and then select \"Account Settings.\"\r\n\r\n\r\nPassword Modification: Access the account settings page to update your password.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nModify Password', 1, '2024-08-29 05:51:47', '2024-08-29 05:51:47', 'd-modify', 'dots-user-documentation', 'version', '', 'Initial publish', 1),
(53, 2, '1.1 Software Overview', '<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-this-is-the-user-gui\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"IF1k2hqAZlgS\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"IF1k2hqAZlgS\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"IF1k2hqAZlgS\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"cFNZhoibcwMe\"><span data-offset-key=\"cFNZhoibcwMe:0\">This is the user guide for our web document management system. It is a powerful tool that will help you work with websites and documents more easily and quickly. This program, which used to be called Dots, is the best way to manage, share, and update papers online from a single, unified platform.</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"IF1k2hqAZlgS\" class=\"relative flex-1\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" data-slate-fragment=\"\" id=\"bkmrk-this-app-streamlines\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"8raa0M1mXqb0\"><span data-offset-key=\"8raa0M1mXqb0:0\">This app streamlines your work and makes you more productive, whether you\'re working on everyday documents or controlling website content directly on the server. You can use a smooth web-based method instead of old-fashioned ones like FTP if the screen is easy to use. The built-in web IDE lets you work on projects online, and the software is flexible enough to fit into any work setting.</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is the user guide for our web document management system. It is a powerful tool that will help you work with websites and documents more easily and quickly. This program, which used to be called Dots, is the best way to manage, share, and update papers online from a single, unified platform.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThis app streamlines your work and makes you more productive, whether you\'re working on everyday documents or controlling website content directly on the server. You can use a smooth web-based method instead of old-fashioned ones like FTP if the screen is easy to use. The built-in web IDE lets you work on projects online, and the software is flexible enough to fit into any work setting.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-08-29 05:52:54', '2024-08-29 05:52:54', '11-software-overview', 'dots-user-documentation', 'version', '', '', 2),
(54, 2, '1.1 Software Overview', '<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-this-is-the-user-gui\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"IF1k2hqAZlgS\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"IF1k2hqAZlgS\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"IF1k2hqAZlgS\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"cFNZhoibcwMe\"><span data-offset-key=\"cFNZhoibcwMe:0\">This is the user guide for our web document management system. It is a powerful tool that will help you work with websites and documents more easily and quickly. This program, which used to be called Dots, is the best way to manage, share, and update papers online from a single, unified platform.</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"IF1k2hqAZlgS\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" data-slate-fragment=\"\" id=\"bkmrk-this-app-streamlines\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\" class=\"relative flex-1\"></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"8raa0M1mXqb0\"><span data-offset-key=\"8raa0M1mXqb0:0\">This app streamlines your work and makes you more productive, whether you\'re working on everyday documents or controlling website content directly on the server. You can use a smooth web-based method instead of old-fashioned ones like FTP if the screen is easy to use. The built-in web IDE lets you work on projects online, and the software is flexible enough to fit into any work setting.</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"SLWdO76yQoDM\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is the user guide for our web document management system. It is a powerful tool that will help you work with websites and documents more easily and quickly. This program, which used to be called Dots, is the best way to manage, share, and update papers online from a single, unified platform.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThis app streamlines your work and makes you more productive, whether you\'re working on everyday documents or controlling website content directly on the server. You can use a smooth web-based method instead of old-fashioned ones like FTP if the screen is easy to use. The built-in web IDE lets you work on projects online, and the software is flexible enough to fit into any work setting.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-08-29 05:53:01', '2024-08-29 05:53:01', '11-software-overview', 'dots-user-documentation', 'version', '', '', 3);
