(64, 10, '3.2 Left Pane', '<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-3.2.1-favorites\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"Dr8aZNNO5IWQ\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"Dr8aZNNO5IWQ\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"Dr8aZNNO5IWQ\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"Ojzdrz7YPm3n\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"Ojzdrz7YPm3n:0\">3.2.1 Favorites</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"Dr8aZNNO5IWQ\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-favorites-overview-t\">\r\n<div data-key=\"5JG9B799awRU\"><span data-key=\"pbCdMyCRWIJM\"><span data-offset-key=\"pbCdMyCRWIJM:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Favorites Overview</span><span data-offset-key=\"pbCdMyCRWIJM:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> The </span><span data-offset-key=\"pbCdMyCRWIJM:2\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Super Path Mode</span><span data-offset-key=\"pbCdMyCRWIJM:3\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> is supported by the system, which allows users to bookmark a variety of elements, including documents, search results, department groups, storage locations, and categories. This function facilitates the rapid and effortless retrieval of frequently utilized items.</span></span></div>\r\n<div data-key=\"5JG9B799awRU\"></div>\r\n<div data-key=\"5JG9B799awRU\" class=\"align-center\"><span data-key=\"pbCdMyCRWIJM\"><span data-offset-key=\"pbCdMyCRWIJM:3\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2024-08/rightp.PNG\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2024-08/scaled-1680-/rightp.PNG\" alt=\"rightp.PNG\" width=\"723\" height=\"326\"></a></span></span></div>\r\n<div data-key=\"5JG9B799awRU\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-3.2.2-directory-navi\">\r\n<div data-key=\"QKSZvNhIWuPH\"><strong><span data-key=\"quo8J24oqv06\"><span data-offset-key=\"quo8J24oqv06:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">3.2.2 Directory Navigation</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div data-key=\"QKSZvNhIWuPH\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-private-space-a-pers\">\r\n<div data-key=\"joG8foB8HRvt\">\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><span data-key=\"DqjZGDY4sncq\"><strong><span data-offset-key=\"DqjZGDY4sncq:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Private Space</span></strong><span data-offset-key=\"DqjZGDY4sncq:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> A personal Space is allocated to each user, which is a private area that is exclusively reserved for their personal files and documents.</span></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><strong><span data-offset-key=\"d7INOOUddCK4:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Disk for Enterprise Networks</span></strong><span data-offset-key=\"d7INOOUddCK4:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"><strong> </strong>The Enterprise Network Disk functions as the public storage space for the entire organization, enabling the sharing of documents and collaboration among teams.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><strong><span data-offset-key=\"yNa9Nf0JU6Mu:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Folder for the Department</span></strong><span data-offset-key=\"yNa9Nf0JU6Mu:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"><strong> </strong>The user\'s department is listed in the \"Department I\'m In\" section. Users can collaborate with colleagues by accessing the department-specific folder by tapping on it.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"Wr9JG6ILs1W5:0\">workplace that is collaborative</strong><span data-offset-key=\"Wr9JG6ILs1W5:1\"> All files that other users have shared with you for collaboration are consolidated in the Collaborate with Me directory. This simplifies the management and accessibility of shared documents by centralizing all collaborative endeavors.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-workplace-that-is-co\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"21Vz8v7wq32t\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"21Vz8v7wq32t\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-3.2.3-direct-access-\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"n2vZCf6eUg7D\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"n2vZCf6eUg7D\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"n2vZCf6eUg7D\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><br></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"n2vZCf6eUg7D\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"GvJ4OsDj7IFE\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"GvJ4OsDj7IFE:0\">3.2.3 Direct Access by Category</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"n2vZCf6eUg7D\" class=\"relative flex-1\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" data-slate-fragment=\"\" id=\"bkmrk-recent-documents-thi\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"NxBZNTeHLqLW\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"NxBZNTeHLqLW\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-4 pb-4 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"NxBZNTeHLqLW\" class=\"relative flex-1\">\r\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"BRnLBcDrsgyj\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"BRnLBcDrsgyj\">\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"jZNDh7KzV21j\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"jZNDh7KzV21j:0\">Recent Documents</strong><span data-offset-key=\"jZNDh7KzV21j:1\"> This section enables users to effectively manage their most recent work by providing fast access to documents that have been recently created, uploaded, or modified.</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"nzZ4ML56ugyZ:0\">My Collaborations</strong><span data-offset-key=\"nzZ4ML56ugyZ:1\"> Users have the ability to manage shared files with a variety of operations, including reverse Selection, Select All, and more, by navigating to Tools &gt; My Collaboration. Once the sharing arrangement is selected, users have the option to modify the sharing permissions, navigate to the parent directory, or terminate it.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"AH7NjEAcor4k:0\">Collaborate with Me</strong><span data-offset-key=\"AH7NjEAcor4k:1\"> Documents that other people have shared with the user are available in this section, which is accessible through Tools &gt; Collaborate with Me. Users have the ability to preview, revise, remark on, manage, and perform other operations on these files, contingent upon the permissions they have been granted.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"ilbXwwJ7EPK5:0\">Recycle Bin</strong><span data-offset-key=\"ilbXwwJ7EPK5:1\"> All files and folders that have been erased are stored in the recycle Bin. Users have the ability to manage their expunged content by performing actions such as Restore, Permanently Delete, and Empty Recycle Bin.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"7tpwJtEPa9gV:0\">File Types</strong><span data-offset-key=\"7tpwJtEPa9gV:1\"> The organization and retrieval of files are simplified through the automatic categorization of files according to their format into categories such as images, documents, videos, compressed packages, music, and others.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"dTD698vLAWnr:0\">File Tags</strong><span data-offset-key=\"dTD698vLAWnr:1\"> File Tags Custom tags can be generated and maintained by users to facilitate the classification and organization of their files for their own benefit. This function is especially beneficial for the speedy access and personalized administration of files.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n3.2.1 Favorites\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFavorites Overview The Super Path Mode is supported by the system, which allows users to bookmark a variety of elements, including documents, search results, department groups, storage locations, and categories. This function facilitates the rapid and effortless retrieval of frequently utilized items.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n3.2.2 Directory Navigation\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPrivate Space A personal Space is allocated to each user, which is a private area that is exclusively reserved for their personal files and documents.\r\nDisk for Enterprise Networks The Enterprise Network Disk functions as the public storage space for the entire organization, enabling the sharing of documents and collaboration among teams.\r\nFolder for the Department The user\'s department is listed in the \"Department I\'m In\" section. Users can collaborate with colleagues by accessing the department-specific folder by tapping on it.\r\nworkplace that is collaborative All files that other users have shared with you for collaboration are consolidated in the Collaborate with Me directory. This simplifies the management and accessibility of shared documents by centralizing all collaborative endeavors.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n3.2.3 Direct Access by Category\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nRecent Documents This section enables users to effectively manage their most recent work by providing fast access to documents that have been recently created, uploaded, or modified.\r\nMy Collaborations Users have the ability to manage shared files with a variety of operations, including reverse Selection, Select All, and more, by navigating to Tools > My Collaboration. Once the sharing arrangement is selected, users have the option to modify the sharing permissions, navigate to the parent directory, or terminate it.\r\nCollaborate with Me Documents that other people have shared with the user are available in this section, which is accessible through Tools > Collaborate with Me. Users have the ability to preview, revise, remark on, manage, and perform other operations on these files, contingent upon the permissions they have been granted.\r\nRecycle Bin All files and folders that have been erased are stored in the recycle Bin. Users have the ability to manage their expunged content by performing actions such as Restore, Permanently Delete, and Empty Recycle Bin.\r\nFile Types The organization and retrieval of files are simplified through the automatic categorization of files according to their format into categories such as images, documents, videos, compressed packages, music, and others.\r\nFile Tags File Tags Custom tags can be generated and maintained by users to facilitate the classification and organization of their files for their own benefit. This function is especially beneficial for the speedy access and personalized administration of files.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-08-29 06:04:51', '2024-08-29 06:04:51', '32-left-pane', 'dots-user-documentation', 'version', '', '', 3);
