n class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"Kb6lvNRF7tgT\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"Kb6lvNRF7tgT:0\">Pinyin Search</strong><span data-offset-key=\"Kb6lvNRF7tgT:1\"> It enables users to search for files by inputting Pinyin, which is a method that is well-known to those who are accustomed to it.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"9oOyDRtND6lT\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"9oOyDRtND6lT\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r r-13awgt0\">\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"5mA5CIFxWaya\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"IsMtKdin0FG5\"><span data-offset-key=\"IsMtKdin0FG5:0\">Search for the first letter It enables queries using the first letters of Pinyin, which is notably beneficial for locating folders, thereby facilitating rapid file retrieval.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-customizing-the-sear\">\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"D2qbozXXY3b6\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\n<div data-key=\"D2qbozXXY3b6\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\n<div data-block-content=\"D2qbozXXY3b6\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><br></div>\n<div data-block-content=\"D2qbozXXY3b6\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"v6ZCP7SgVWI6\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"v6ZCP7SgVWI6:0\">Customizing the Search Scope:</strong></span></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-current-folder%2Fall-f\">\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"hapbaLVygqiz\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\n<div data-key=\"hapbaLVygqiz\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-4 pb-4 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\n<div data-block-content=\"hapbaLVygqiz\" class=\"relative flex-1\">\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"kE3X6IN0BPgs\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"kE3X6IN0BPgs\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r r-13awgt0\">\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"t6oA9mCXyM7k\"><br></div>\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"t6oA9mCXyM7k\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"5TYwAYeoyqiM\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"5TYwAYeoyqiM:0\">Current Folder/All Folders</strong><span data-offset-key=\"5TYwAYeoyqiM:1\"> Users have the ability to determine whether the search should be limited to the current folder or extend across all folders, thereby improving the precision of the search.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-file-type-filtering%3A\">\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"VexC9SF3ncM8\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\n<div data-key=\"VexC9SF3ncM8\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\n<div data-block-content=\"VexC9SF3ncM8\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><br></div>\n<div data-block-content=\"VexC9SF3ncM8\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"jFqlqZHSoY44\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"jFqlqZHSoY44:0\">File Type Filtering</strong><span data-offset-key=\"jFqlqZHSoY44:1\">:</span></span></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-preset-file-categori\">\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"aHc0qi6r4TtS\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\n<div data-key=\"aHc0qi6r4TtS\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-4 pb-4 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\n<div data-block-content=\"aHc0qi6r4TtS\" class=\"relative flex-1\">\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"lyo86wKCwGZs\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"lyo86wKCwGZs\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r r-13awgt0\">\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"IHpwdUDscbeJ\"><br></div>\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"IHpwdUDscbeJ\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"aVKlcolpHTPq\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"aVKlcolpHTPq:0\">Preset File Categories</strong><span data-offset-key=\"aVKlcolpHTPq:1\"> The system organizes files into folders, documents, images, music, videos, and more. Additionally, users have the ability to establish their own file formats in order to conduct more precise searches.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-time-range-search%3A\">\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"zpEWeZPmkUZH\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\n<div data-key=\"zpEWeZPmkUZH\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\n<div data-block-content=\"zpEWeZPmkUZH\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><br></div>\n<div data-block-content=\"zpEWeZPmkUZH\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"SYLkTndYZMkD\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"SYLkTndYZMkD:0\">Time Range Search</strong><span data-offset-key=\"SYLkTndYZMkD:1\">:</span></span></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-date-of-creation-use\">\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"TQLrfA1gNNe9\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\n<div data-key=\"TQLrfA1gNNe9\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-4 pb-4 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\n<div data-block-content=\"TQLrfA1gNNe9\" class=\"relative flex-1\">\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"fQQNI38mDug1\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"fQQNI38mDug1\">\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r r-13awgt0\">\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"wDCDTPyC0BDh\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"zEOqeuJ1s6GJ\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"zEOqeuJ1s6GJ:0\">Date of Creation</strong><span data-offset-key=\"zEOqeuJ1s6GJ:1\"> Users can simplify the process of locating files by specifying a time range for file creation, which simplifies the process of determining the date of their creation.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-file-size-filtering%3A\">\n<div data-key=\"8VDGniwlIcjh\"><strong><span data-key=\"XOVazjBLJj7w\"><span data-offset-key=\"XOVazjBLJj7w:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">File Size Filtering</span><span data-offset-key=\"XOVazjBLJj7w:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">:</span></span></strong></div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-search-based-on-file\">\n<div data-key=\"nur0ewSuiPJE\">\n<div data-key=\"xmpkm8mxrA3t\">\n<div data-key=\"6AiXPkpFnULd\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"null\"><span data-key=\"EPSOiIreApNG\"><span data-offset-key=\"EPSOiIreApNG:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Search Based on File Size</span><span data-offset-key=\"EPSOiIreApNG:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Users can locate files of a specific size or within a defined range by filtering search results by file size.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-creator-based-search\">\n<div data-key=\"38AKn906Wl9J\"><strong><span data-key=\"B5a1aPzDAVgS\"><span data-offset-key=\"B5a1aPzDAVgS:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Creator-Based Search</span><span data-offset-key=\"B5a1aPzDAVgS:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">:</span></span></strong></div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-departmental-network\">\n<div data-key=\"7aAe8mi2485Z\">\n<div data-key=\"znfC55M8SQ4M\">\n<div data-key=\"L7E8TYpVSuat\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"null\"><span data-key=\"Bd0GCX6zeRQn\"><span data-offset-key=\"Bd0GCX6zeRQn:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Departmental Network Disk</span><span data-offset-key=\"Bd0GCX6zeRQn:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Users have the ability to search for files that were generated by a particular individual in the enterprise environment, which is especially beneficial for team collaborations.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div data-key=\"L7E8TYpVSuat\"><br></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-3.3.2-options-for-fi\">\n<div data-key=\"FmIp78BQx1nH\"><strong><span data-key=\"JNmrWGbtjG0K\"><span data-offset-key=\"JNmrWGbtjG0K:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">3.3.2 Options for File Viewing</span></span></strong></div>\n</div>\n<div data-key=\"FmIp78BQx1nH\" id=\"bkmrk-\"></div>\n<div data-key=\"FmIp78BQx1nH\" id=\"bkmrk--1\"></div>\n<div data-key=\"FmIp78BQx1nH\" id=\"bkmrk--2\"></div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-file-management-view\">\n<div data-key=\"rK31WHjfvp3G\"><br></div>\n<div data-key=\"rK31WHjfvp3G\"><span data-key=\"HLbGgGfvCgRq\"><span data-offset-key=\"HLbGgGfvCgRq:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">File Management View Modes</span><span data-offset-key=\"HLbGgGfvCgRq:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Within the file administration module of the Kedao Cloud system, there are three distinct viewing modes: List View, Icon View, and </span><span data-offset-key=\"HLbGgGfvCgRq:2\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Column View</span><span data-offset-key=\"HLbGgGfvCgRq:3\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">.</span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-icon-mode-images-are\">\n<div data-key=\"EinAxL3ahUTW\">\n<div data-key=\"W30xVD6iv49E\">\n<div data-key=\"o4RvZj5QUcLt\"><span data-key=\"yoiW6ePVde5f\"><span data-offset-key=\"yoiW6ePVde5f:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Icon Mode</span><span data-offset-key=\"yoiW6ePVde5f:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Images are automatically displayed as thumbnails in this mode, in addition to a variety of file icons. Users can effortlessly modify the dimensions of the icon and organize files according to their preferences.</span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div data-key=\"gYJuZKBqKtzj\">\n<div data-key=\"T36ZmQPP6nMv\"><span data-key=\"Cj1DK4yVMHAp\"><span data-offset-key=\"Cj1DK4yVMHAp:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">List Mode</span><span data-offset-key=\"Cj1DK4yVMHAp:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> List Mode provides a methodical approach to file management. Customizable alterations, such as the capacity to resize and drag the title bar, and the unlimited expansion of folders with subdirectories, are supported.</span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div data-key=\"kDQ2Hm3bZPPZ\">\n<div data-key=\"MoBt4LdFjGAD\"><span data-key=\"NXSacNfTBxx5\"><span data-offset-key=\"NXSacNfTBxx5:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Column Mode</span><span data-offset-key=\"NXSacNfTBxx5:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Column Mode, which is modeled after the Mac OS interface, enables users to expand multi-level folders in columns. The administration of intricate folder hierarchies is substantially simplified by the ease with which files can be transferred between columns.</span></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-key=\"MoBt4LdFjGAD\" id=\"bkmrk--3\"><span data-key=\"NXSacNfTBxx5\"><span data-offset-key=\"NXSacNfTBxx5:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"><br></span></span></div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-3.3.3-information-%28p\">\n<div data-key=\"AwUroBPfIPZI\"><strong><span data-key=\"ByiPGfi3XVCg\"><span data-offset-key=\"ByiPGfi3XVCg:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">3.3.3 Information (Properties) Panel</span></span></strong></div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-attributes-overview%3A\">\n<div data-key=\"MGXU852LRj0l\"><strong><span data-key=\"3cwOEtvnM26H\"><span data-offset-key=\"3cwOEtvnM26H:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Attributes Overview</span><span data-offset-key=\"3cwOEtvnM26H:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">:</span></span></strong></div>\n<div data-key=\"MGXU852LRj0l\"><br></div>\n</div>\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" data-slate-fragment=\"\" id=\"bkmrk-fundamental-informat\">\n<div data-key=\"Qd9Az1XBUbwf\">\n<div data-key=\"87D0qxU2ro7E\">\n<div data-key=\"WaaSecIgqmOS\"><span data-key=\"5WvhfRaUxLLR\"><span data-offset-key=\"5WvhfRaUxLLR:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Fundamental Information</span><span data-offset-key=\"5WvhfRaUxLLR:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Displays critical file information, including the size, file count, creator/modifier, personal notes, and keywords.</span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div data-key=\"LBAa6CCMqiXH\">\n<div data-key=\"EurpqlpvKhS7\"><span data-key=\"6OW9ghqp7nS0\"><span data-offset-key=\"6OW9ghqp7nS0:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Document Permissions</span><span data-offset-key=\"6OW9ghqp7nS0:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Clarifies the actions that the user is permitted to take by specifying the specific permissions that have been granted to the document.</span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div data-key=\"Dg8WYIaATvyL\">\n<div data-key=\"aOMy5Ki3XzOI\"><span data-key=\"CQsQqbwjrLCt\"><span data-offset-key=\"CQsQqbwjrLCt:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">File Activity</span><span data-offset-key=\"CQsQqbwjrLCt:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Provides a comprehensive record of file dynamics by tracking the history of file actions, such as uploads, modifications, and downloads.</span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div data-key=\"Ct6yqVKJonnS\">\n<div data-key=\"UevHb1gyLGQA\"><span data-key=\"8vhAlHNhTVrv\"><span data-offset-key=\"8vhAlHNhTVrv:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Version History</span><span data-offset-key=\"8vhAlHNhTVrv:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Records all modifications to the file, including the modifier, modification time, and version history, for future reference.</span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div data-key=\"lBwlC4a3f7Q6\">\n<div data-key=\"M5naFwSdwXBd\"><span data-key=\"43iStrf6o4bo\"><span data-offset-key=\"43iStrf6o4bo:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Related Information</span><span data-offset-key=\"43iStrf6o4bo:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> It indicates whether the file is linked to other files, which is essential for comprehending file dependencies.</span></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', '', 1, '2024-08-29 06:29:11', '2024-08-29 06:29:11', '33-right-pane', 'dots-user-documentation', 'update_draft', '', NULL, 0);
