ex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"7tGqfhCO2Kvh\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"uXyJIF1Fva6A\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"uXyJIF1Fva6A:0\">Downloading Methods</strong></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-1.-toolbar-download-\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"Qr7rW9L04urJ\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"Qr7rW9L04urJ\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-4 pb-4 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"Qr7rW9L04urJ\" class=\"relative flex-1\">\r\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"XkdehpulK8gG\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"XkdehpulK8gG\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"OLMjJEgk5ROi\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"OLMjJEgk5ROi:0\">1. Toolbar Download</strong><span data-offset-key=\"OLMjJEgk5ROi:1\"> Select the desired file and click the </span><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"OLMjJEgk5ROi:2\">\"Download\"</strong><span data-offset-key=\"OLMjJEgk5ROi:3\"> button in the toolbar to save the file to your local computer.</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"relative w-full\" node=\"eHibFJSDZfIe\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex\" data-block-content=\"eHibFJSDZfIe\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"EL3RdWsaHILp\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"EL3RdWsaHILp:0\">2.Context Menu Download</strong><span data-offset-key=\"EL3RdWsaHILp:1\"> Alternatively, right-click on the target file, select </span><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"EL3RdWsaHILp:2\">\"Download\"</strong><span data-offset-key=\"EL3RdWsaHILp:3\"> from the context menu, and the file will be downloaded to your local system.</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" data-slate-fragment=\"\" id=\"bkmrk-automatic-compressio\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"hNiAot4T40at\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"hNiAot4T40at\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"hNiAot4T40at\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"Wcl1skiIVUZP\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"Wcl1skiIVUZP:0\">Automatic Compression</strong><span data-offset-key=\"Wcl1skiIVUZP:1\"> Kedao Cloud supports the automatic compression of folders and multiple files during the download process. This feature helps to streamline the download of large quantities of data.</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.2.1 Uploading Files and Folders\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nUploading Methods\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Drag and Drop Upload Users can upload files and folders by dragging them directly from their PC and dropping them into any area of the Kedao Cloud page within the browser. This intuitive method allows for quick and easy file uploads.\r\n2. Click to Upload Alternatively, users can click on the \"Upload\" button in the toolbar of the network disk page. Select \"Select File\" from the dropdown menu to open a file selection dialog where users can choose the file(s) to upload.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nUploading Folders To upload a folder, click on the \"Upload\" button, select the dropdown menu, and choose \"Folder\". Then, select the desired folder from the pop-up window to begin the upload process.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n3. Batch Upload The system supports batch uploading, allowing users to upload multiple files simultaneously. It also facilitates direct folder uploads, making large-scale uploads efficient.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4. Advanced Upload Features\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBreakpoint Resume: The system supports restarting interrupted uploads and fragment uploads, ensuring that large files can be uploaded in multiple parts without losing progress.\r\nFile Transfer Speed: Upload speeds are optimized, allowing files to be transferred quickly and efficiently.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.2.2 Offline Download\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDownloading Files Offline To download files offline, click on the \"Upload\" button dropdown menu on the network disk page and select \"Offline Download.\". Enter the HTTP link of the file you wish to download to initiate the offline download process.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.2.3 Downloading Files\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDownloading Methods\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Toolbar Download Select the desired file and click the \"Download\" button in the toolbar to save the file to your local computer.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n2.Context Menu Download Alternatively, right-click on the target file, select \"Download\" from the context menu, and the file will be downloaded to your local system.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAutomatic Compression Kedao Cloud supports the automatic compression of folders and multiple files during the download process. This feature helps to streamline the download of large quantities of data.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-08-29 07:12:41', '2024-08-29 07:12:41', '42-upload-and-downloads', 'dots-user-documentation', 'version', '', 'Initial publish', 1);
