rsor will automatically focus on the folder name, allowing for immediate renaming. Click outside the folder name area to save the new name.</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-2.-create-a-new-file\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"6D6zHhZJHAE4\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"6D6zHhZJHAE4\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"6D6zHhZJHAE4\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"dxQvHxBcgX5r\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"dxQvHxBcgX5r:0\">2. Create a New File</strong><span data-offset-key=\"dxQvHxBcgX5r:1\"> Click the dropdown menu next to the </span><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"dxQvHxBcgX5r:2\">\"New Folder\"</strong><span data-offset-key=\"dxQvHxBcgX5r:3\"> button and select the desired file format to create a new file in that format.</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"6D6zHhZJHAE4\" class=\"relative flex-1\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-4.3.2-renaming-files\">\r\n<div class=\"page-block-swagger:ml-0 relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[--block-wrapper-max-width]\" node=\"eW7bUz7jB1Cb\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r\">\r\n<div data-key=\"eW7bUz7jB1Cb\" class=\"relative flex py-4 pt-2 pb-2 _dropHorizontal_2u9k6_23\">\r\n<div data-block-content=\"eW7bUz7jB1Cb\" class=\"relative flex-1\"></div>\r\n<div data-block-content=\"eW7bUz7jB1Cb\" class=\"relative flex-1\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"4YCPm7zsEKaM\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"4YCPm7zsEKaM:0\">4.3.2 Renaming Files and Folders</strong></span></sp