\">\r\n<div class=\"css-175oi2r r-13awgt0\">\r\n<div class=\"relative\" data-key=\"xLYdEkxoJ4ul\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><span class=\"select-text text-left text-content-paragraph\"><span data-key=\"zcubjJaEEWCm\"><strong class=\"r-crgep1 r-b88u0q\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-offset-key=\"zcubjJaEEWCm:0\">Tracking Document Changes</strong><span data-offset-key=\"zcubjJaEEWCm:1\"> View a comprehensive history of document changes from upload to deletion. The document dynamics feature records the operator and timestamp of each change.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0-2\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-4.5.5-document-comme\">\r\n<div data-key=\"MCm8cvJqSW24\"><strong><span data-key=\"FPyfRogDnezj\"><span data-offset-key=\"FPyfRogDnezj:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">4.5.5 Document Comments</span></span></strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-comment-tracking-mai\">\r\n<div data-key=\"65Augr7KpglA\">\r\n<div data-key=\"qFH3Mg9oE6kL\">\r\n<div data-key=\"ZS0B6bPORIBk\"><span data-key=\"aY60Ppn9Zrvd\"><span data-offset-key=\"aY60Ppn9Zrvd:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Comment Tracking</span><span data-offset-key=\"aY60Ppn9Zrvd:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Maintain a record of all comments related to document changes. This feature helps track feedback and discussions about the document\'s content.</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-key=\"ZS0B6bPORIBk\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" id=\"bkmrk-4.5.6-view-history\">\r\n<div data-key=\"VCe4qhtx9dHV\"></div>\r\n<div data-key=\"VCe4qhtx9dHV\"><strong><span data-key=\"79dr47geb0dM\"><span data-offset-key=\"79dr47geb0dM:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">4.5.6 View History</span></span></strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-virtualparent=\"true\" data-slate-fragment=\"\" id=\"bkmrk-accessing-historical\">\r\n<div data-key=\"Nm7b9ABj2xZ9\">\r\n<div data-key=\"fwkhihZF6Uo3\">\r\n<div data-key=\"LvqkdnZ5AeBn\"><span data-key=\"6l1Ssy9I9bNX\"><span data-offset-key=\"6l1Ssy9I9bNX:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Accessing Historical Versions</span><span data-offset-key=\"6l1Ssy9I9bNX:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Kedao Cloud automatically archives historical versions of files when changes are made. To view historical versions:</span></span></div>\r\n<div data-key=\"CWaQ6tDcLsHm\">\r\n<div data-key=\"12v9n5C87uMZ\">\r\n<div data-key=\"8Acu29RFvtdZ\"><span data-key=\"riMXLXLx6vys\"><span data-offset-key=\"riMXLXLx6vys:0\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">Right-Click Menu</span><span data-offset-key=\"riMXLXLx6vys:1\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> Select the file, right-click, and choose </span><span data-offset-key=\"riMXLXLx6vys:2\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\">\"View History\"</span><span data-offset-key=\"riMXLXLx6vys:3\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\"> from the menu to access and manage past versions. Options include downloading or rolling back to previous versions.</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.5.1 Internal Collaboration and Sharing\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSharing Documents Internally Users can share documents with specific users or departments within the organization. Define permissions to control access levels for each user or department.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSearch Functionality Use Pinyin or initial letter search to quickly find users or departments.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nHint: Once internal collaboration is initiated, the recipient can view the shared document under \"Collaborate with Me.\"\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.5.2 External Link Sharing\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSharing Files Externally Enable external link sharing to allow users outside the system to access your files.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCustomizable Settings Configure various settings for shared files, including extraction passwords, expiration times, and permission levels to ensure secure and controlled access.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.5.3 Edit Lock\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nLocking Documents Use the document locking feature to prevent simultaneous editing and ensure the integrity of your work. This function is ideal for documents that require single-user editing to avoid conflicts.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.5.4 Document Dynamics\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTracking Document Changes View a comprehensive history of document changes from upload to deletion. The document dynamics feature records the operator and timestamp of each change.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.5.5 Document Comments\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nComment Tracking Maintain a record of all comments related to document changes. This feature helps track feedback and discussions about the document\'s content.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4.5.6 View History\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAccessing Historical Versions Kedao Cloud automatically archives historical versions of files when changes are made. To view historical versions:\r\n\r\n\r\nRight-Click Menu Select the file, right-click, and choose \"View History\" from the menu to access and manage past versions. Options include downloading or rolling back to previous versions.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-08-29 07:24:17', '2024-08-29 07:24:17', '45-sharing-and-collaboration', 'dots-user-documentation', 'version', '', 'Initial publish', 1);
